---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Synapse 学院 — Multi-Agents Academy"
  description="5分钟接入一套完整的AI专家团队体系。53位AI Agent、14+个Skills工作流、四级决策体系，开箱即用。"
>

  <!-- ── Hero ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A1628 0%, #0d1f3c 50%, #011f5c 100%); min-height: 480px;">
    <div class="grid-dots"></div>
    <div class="glow-gold" style="top:-100px; left:-100px; opacity:0.6;"></div>
    <div class="glow-cyan" style="bottom:-80px; right:-80px; opacity:0.5;"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-[#FCAD2A]/30 bg-[#FCAD2A]/10 mb-6">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#FCAD2A] pulse"></span>
        <span class="text-[#FCAD2A] text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">Synapse Multi-Agents 学院</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-5 leading-tight">
        5分钟拥有一支<br>
        <span style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #FCAD2A, #028CDC); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;">完整的 AI 专家团队</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="text-white/60 text-lg mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        53位AI Agent × 14+个Skills工作流 × 四级决策体系<br>
        clone一次，立即运行。不需要任何配置经验。
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 mb-14">
        <a href="/academy/get-synapse" class="px-8 py-3.5 bg-[#FCAD2A] text-[#0A1628] rounded-lg font-bold hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
          免费获取 Synapse →
        </a>
        <a href="/academy/learn" class="px-8 py-3.5 bg-white/10 text-white rounded-lg font-semibold border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/15 transition-colors">
          了解方法论
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Stats strip -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        {[
          { num: "53", label: "AI Agent" },
          { num: "14+", label: "Skills 工作流" },
          { num: "4级", label: "决策体系" },
        ].map(s => (
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 py-4">
            <div class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#FCAD2A]">{s.num}</div>
            <div class="text-white/50 text-xs mt-1">{s.label}</div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="glow-line"></div>

  <!-- ── Nav cards (sub-pages) ──────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest text-[#028CDC] uppercase mb-3 text-center">学院导航</p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] text-center mb-10">选择你的起点</h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
      <!-- Get Synapse -->
      <a href="/academy/get-synapse" class="card-glow group block p-6 bg-white border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-xl accent-top-gold hover:border-[#FCAD2A]/40">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#FCAD2A]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-[#FCAD2A]/20 transition-colors">
          <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="#FCAD2A" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 16l4-4m0 0l-4-4m4 4H8"/><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-1">获取 Synapse</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">免费 clone → 3步个性化 → 5分钟上手</p>
        <div class="mt-4 text-xs font-semibold text-[#FCAD2A]">免费 →</div>
      </a>

      <!-- Team -->
      <a href="/academy/team" class="card-glow group block p-6 bg-white border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-xl accent-top-cyan hover:border-[#028CDC]/40">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#028CDC]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-[#028CDC]/20 transition-colors">
          <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="#028CDC" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-1">AI 团队名录</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">53位专家 · 13个模块 · 能力图谱全览</p>
        <div class="mt-4 text-xs font-semibold text-[#028CDC]">浏览团队 →</div>
      </a>

      <!-- Skills -->
      <a href="/academy/skills" class="card-glow group block p-6 bg-white border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-xl accent-top-blue hover:border-[#013A7D]/40">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#013A7D]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-[#013A7D]/20 transition-colors">
          <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="#013A7D" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-1">Skills 工作流库</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">14+个内置工作流 · /dispatch · /qa-gate</p>
        <div class="mt-4 text-xs font-semibold text-[#013A7D]">查看全部 →</div>
      </a>

      <!-- Learn -->
      <a href="/academy/learn" class="card-glow group block p-6 bg-white border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-xl accent-top-gold hover:border-[#FCAD2A]/40">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#FCAD2A]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-[#FCAD2A]/20 transition-colors">
          <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="#FCAD2A" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-1">Harness 方法论</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">5项核心原则 · 为什么 Agent = Model + Harness</p>
        <div class="mt-4 text-xs font-semibold text-[#FCAD2A]">开始学习 →</div>
      </a>

    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="glow-line"></div>

  <!-- ── Pricing redirect ────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest text-[#028CDC] uppercase mb-3 text-center">定价</p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] text-center mb-4">体系免费 · 服务收费</h2>
    <p class="text-[var(--color-text-light)] text-center max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8">
      Synapse 体系本身完全免费开源。咨询、实施、培训等专业服务的定价信息已统一搬到 Synapse 定价页。
    </p>
    <div class="text-center">
      <a href="/synapse/pricing" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-[#FCAD2A] text-[#0A1628] rounded-lg font-bold hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
        查看完整定价 →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="glow-line"></div>

  <!-- ── What's inside ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-16" style="background: #F7F8FA;">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest text-[#028CDC] uppercase mb-3 text-center">体系资产</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] text-center mb-10">你获得的完整体系</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl">🧠</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-[var(--color-text)]">Harness Configuration</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)]">CLAUDE.md — 体系控制中枢</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-light)]">定义CEO执行链、四级决策体系、团队派单制度、跨会话状态管理。Harness Engineering 的核心载体。</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl">👥</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-[var(--color-text)]">53位AI专家</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)]">13个模块 · 全能力覆盖</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-light)]">战略/研发/运营/内容/成长/情报/HR。每位专家有具体能力描述（B级及以上标准），审计评分≥90分。</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl">⚡</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-[var(--color-text)]">14+ Skills 工作流</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)]">一句话触发结构化流程</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-light)]">/dispatch 派单 · /qa-gate 质量门禁 · /retro 复盘 · /graphify 智囊分析 · /dev-plan 开发计划等。</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl">📊</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-[var(--color-text)]">HR管理引擎</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)]">hr_base.py · 自动审计</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-light)]">自动评分（≥90分合格）、能力分级（A/B/C）、入职审批、跨会话状态追踪。一套完整的AI团队治理体系。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── CTA ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-20" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A1628 0%, #011f5c 100%);">
    <div class="grid-dots" style="opacity:0.5;"></div>
    <div class="glow-gold" style="top:-50px; right:10%; opacity:0.4;"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4">
        准备好了吗？<br>
        <span style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #FCAD2A, #028CDC); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;">5分钟后你就有一支AI团队</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-white/50 mb-8">完全免费 · 本地运行 · 数据不经过任何第三方</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/academy/get-synapse" class="px-8 py-3.5 bg-[#FCAD2A] text-[#0A1628] rounded-lg font-bold hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
          立即获取 Synapse →
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/lysanderl-glitch/synapse" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="px-8 py-3.5 bg-white/10 text-white rounded-lg font-semibold border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/15 transition-colors">
          GitHub →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
